snippet.title: Ground Control Anthology - Official Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ground Control Anthology is available now on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/254820

In the far future of the Ground Control series, mega-corporations have taken to the stars to fight over colonized planets. Your task is to lead armies of advanced ground and air units onto the terrains of distant worlds, and fight for control as war threatens to overwhelm the universe. 

Ground Control Anthology and Ground Control II: Operation Exodus are available now on Steam, and you can buy them together for less in the Ground Control Collection.
